FROM (
    SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[ArticleCategory], [a].[Material], [a].[Name], [a].[NetWeight]
    FROM [Articles] AS [a]
    ORDER BY (SELECT 1)
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [a1]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[ArticlesId], [a0].[BicycleCategoriesId], [b].[Id], [b].[Name]
    FROM [ArticleBicycleCategory] AS [a0]
    INNER JOIN [BicycleCategories] AS [b] ON [a0].[BicycleCategoriesId] = [b].[Id]
) AS [s] ON [a1].[Id] = [s].[ArticlesId]
ORDER BY [a1].[Id], [s].[ArticlesId], [s].[BicycleCategoriesId]

SELECT [a1].[Id], [a1].[ArticleCategory], [a1].[Material], [a1].[Name], [a1].[NetWeight], [s].[ArticlesId], [s].[BicycleCategoriesId], [s].[Id], [s].[Name]
FROM (
    SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[ArticleCategory], [a].[Material], [a].[Name], [a].[NetWeight]
    FROM [Articles] AS [a]
    ORDER BY [a].[NetWeight]
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [a1]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[ArticlesId], [a0].[BicycleCategoriesId], [b].[Id], [b].[Name]
    FROM [ArticleBicycleCategory] AS [a0]
    INNER JOIN [BicycleCategories] AS [b] ON [a0].[BicycleCategoriesId] = [b].[Id]
) AS [s] ON [a1].[Id] = [s].[ArticlesId]
ORDER BY [a1].[NetWeight], [a1].[Id], [s].[ArticlesId], [s].[BicycleCategoriesId]

FROM (
    SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[ArticleCategory], [a].[Material], [a].[Name], [a].[NetWeight]
    FROM [Articles] AS [a]
    ORDER BY [a].[NetWeight]
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [a1]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[ArticlesId], [a0].[BicycleCategoriesId], [b].[Id], [b].[Name]
    FROM [ArticleBicycleCategory] AS [a0]
    INNER JOIN [BicycleCategories] AS [b] ON [a0].[BicycleCategoriesId] = [b].[Id]
) AS [s] ON [a1].[Id] = [s].[ArticlesId]

FROM (
    SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[ArticleCategory], [a].[Material], [a].[Name], [a].[NetWeight]
    FROM [Articles] AS [a]
    ORDER BY [a].[NetWeight] DESC
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [a1]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[ArticlesId], [a0].[BicycleCategoriesId], [b].[Id], [b].[Name]

) AS [s] ON [a1].[Id] = [s].[ArticlesId]

SELECT [a1].[Id], [a1].[ArticleCategory], [a1].[ArticleNumber], [a1].[Height], [a1].[Length], [a1].[Material], [a1].[Name], [a1].[NetWeight], [a1].[Width], [s].[ArticlesId], [s].[BicycleCategoriesId], [s].[Id], [s].[Name]
FROM (
    SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[ArticleCategory], [a].[ArticleNumber], [a].[Height], [a].[Length], [a].[Material], [a].[Name], [a].[NetWeight], [a].[Width]
    FROM [Articles] AS [a]
    ORDER BY [a].[NetWeight]
    OFFSET @__p_0 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_1 ROWS ONLY
) AS [a1]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [a0].[ArticlesId], [a0].[BicycleCategoriesId], [b].[Id], [b].[Name]
    FROM [ArticleBicycleCategory] AS [a0]
    INNER JOIN [BicycleCategories] AS [b] ON [a0].[BicycleCategoriesId] = [b].[Id]
) AS [s] ON [a1].[Id] = [s].[ArticlesId]

    SELECT [a].[Id], [a].[ArticleCategory], [a].[ArticleNumber], [a].[Height], [a].[Length], [a].[Material], [a].[Name], [a].[NetWeight], [a].[Width]
